silver_manulcooky:manulcooky:1:3:false:60:tickwin.ogg:Manual boost! You gained %amount% manual cookies!
silver_speed:cookyspeed:5:15:false:40:tickwin.ogg:Speed scratch! Your baking speed increased by %amount%ms!

